    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347320/extras/190daa1a07aabaf156ee3fe34ddc4cc0.poster.avif?t=1720887157\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347320/extras/190daa1a07aabaf156ee3fe34ddc4cc0.webm?t=1720887157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347320/extras/190daa1a07aabaf156ee3fe34ddc4cc0.mp4?t=1720887157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Aim Trainers in VR tend to never be useful and are always short with what they offer and lack enough customization to be personalized.<br><br>Dirty Aim Trainer VR &quot;aims&quot; to be immersive and easy to use while offering the best training sessions any VR Aim Trainer can offer. <br><br>With multiple tasks improving flicking, tracking, reaction time, peaking, holding angles, tracking and much more. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347320/extras/70d723f24fc3b5212bae7b7b0833bd81.poster.avif?t=1720887157\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347320/extras/70d723f24fc3b5212bae7b7b0833bd81.webm?t=1720887157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347320/extras/70d723f24fc3b5212bae7b7b0833bd81.mp4?t=1720887157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You should have no problem finding the task that helps work on the problem your having, and getting personal based feedback. <br><br>Want custom music to train to? With a custom music system you can easily import any mp3 files into the game. <br><br>Dirty Aim VR tries it's best to be relaxing but effective at the same time.<br><br>We understand the struggle of learning VR Shooters and that's something Dirty Aim VR hopes to help and make the process easier for beginners or hardcore players.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347320/extras/e729d7daae99ff68e1005adc15c8cbe9.poster.avif?t=1720887157\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347320/extras/e729d7daae99ff68e1005adc15c8cbe9.webm?t=1720887157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347320/extras/e729d7daae99ff68e1005adc15c8cbe9.mp4?t=1720887157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
